comments.body: [~jerome] Do you have any concern about me consolidating the zoomed in component for RE and non-RE VIP. I know the banner has moved because of it. Instead of being the second of the photo, it'll become sticky instead. This helps with code maintenance in the future though. Please provide new key-value pair if needed.
[~leslava]  - I will reach out to you on this ticket. We may need new key value pairs for non-real estate VIP

If the banner stays in the gallery, it will be the same we have now,

MREC_1_GAL_D for Desktop and MREC_1_GAL_M for Mobile

[~homer]  good question and i support the decision since it makes more sense for user. 

[~leslava] [~jseverins] you want to compare the current carousel banner and the new design on RE VIP? Think it's a good learning how much impact we got. Besides, i assume we should use the same KV for this banner.

Hi, yes we should use the same KV we have on Gallery VIP.

For the comparison, las 30 days I had better performance metrics on REVIP(gallery banners), but the impressions aren't to big, so if we can improve the impression we could make more money

[^Gallery_VIP_REVIP_Revenue.xlsx]
We should use another AdPos for the leaderboard like we have it in REVIP, the key-value will be  *LB_1_GAL_D*

[~jerome] two questions: Cc [~allen]
 # For the original VIP gallery ad (see attached follow below), since we have the vertical one on the right of the gallery page, do we feel comfortable of taking this squared one off for Desktop? 
 # Want to double check that if we are still keeping the square one on mobile.  
 # Adding leaderboard like REVIP for this VIP ticket? (see Luis comment above)? Raymond, could you please help me understand more about all current leaderboard placements on diverse VIPs?[!https://files.slack.com/files-tmb/T3U2DUYG4-FBKCHHABT-465679e809/screen_shot_2018-07-06_at_4.15.16_pm_720.png!|https://files.slack.com/files-pri/T3U2DUYG4-FBKCHHABT/screen_shot_2018-07-06_at_4.15.16_pm.png]

Hi [~john], we will keep a leaderboard inside the gallery for bigger resolution and one in the bottom of *VIP* page, as we have it now in REVIP, the key-value for the leadeboard at the bottom will be: *LB_1_BVIP_D*

Please consider this.

Hi [~leslava], we didn't change the leaderboard, so it will still be there. For the MREC in the gallery on VIP, we will keep it for now. Since this ticket is only about the VIP gallery, if we need to make VIP share the REVIP page structure and banners, we will open another ticket later. [~allen]
